  "prompt": "What is Instagram's hourly comment limit?",
  "response": "As of my last update, Instagram doesn't publicly disclose specific limits for hourly comments or other engagement actions to prevent spammy behavior. However, users generally report that Instagram imposes limits to diminish the likelihood of spammy activity, which can range from a few dozen to a couple hundred comments per hour, depending on various factors such as account age, follower count, and previous behavior.\n\nIf you're actively engaging on the platform, it's a good idea to proceed with moderation and avoid excessive commenting in a short period to ensure your account remains in good standing and doesn\u2019t receive restrictions. For the most accurate and up-to-date information on limits, consider checking Instagram's official guidelines or user support resources.",
